fields.name: task-launch
fields.title: Task Launch
fields.description: A task for this job failed to launch.

fields.name: docker-task-launch
fields.title: Docker Launch
fields.description: A task for this job failed to launch a Docker container.

fields.name: docker-terminated
fields.title: Docker Terminated
fields.description: A Docker container for this job terminated unexpectedly.

fields.name: node-lost
fields.title: Node Lost
fields.description: The node running this job was lost.

fields.name: launch-timeout
fields.title: Launch Timeout
fields.description: A task for this job failed to start within a reasonable amount of time after being launched. Please contact a Scale administrator to diagnose the problem.

fields.name: pre-timeout
fields.title: Pre-task Timeout
fields.description: The pre-task did not finish within a reasonable amount of time. This is likely due to excessive time downloading the algorithm's input data from their workspace(s).

fields.name: post-timeout
fields.title: Post-task Timeout
fields.description: The post-task did not finish within a reasonable amount of time. This is likely due to excessive time uploading the algorithm's output data to their workspace(s).

fields.name: timeout
fields.title: Timeout
fields.description: The algorithm exceeded its timeout threshold.

fields.name: algorithm-unknown
fields.title: Algorithm Failure
fields.description: The algorithm failed by returning a non-zero exit code. To allow Scale to detect more specific problems with the algorithm, please define the appropriate errors for the non-zero exit codes that the algorithm may return.

fields.name: invalid-results-manifest
fields.title: Invalid Results Manifest
fields.description: The algorithm produced an invalid results manifest file. Please see the job log for more information.

fields.name: missing-required-output
fields.title: Missing Required Output
fields.description: The algorithm failed to produce a required output. Please see the job log for more information.

fields.name: missing-setting
fields.title: Missing Setting
fields.description: The job is missing a required settings value. Please define default values for all settings required by this job type.
